{"tid":1686302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[黃色經濟圈危機]唔該唔好再亂咁幫人貼米豬連啦","createTime":"2019-11-01T04:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T03:21:12.000Z","uid":78349,"like":109,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"db533b3785bbe82991e6db81ee21ff4a5d89f9bb","tid":1686302,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:47:54.000Z","msg":"呢啲時勢貼個貼紙排隊排到仆街<br />\n你問個老細好唔好佢lur 飯應啦<br />\n<br />\n黃店認證唔係支持五大訴求咁簡單<br />\n個d 係可以幫襯<br />\n係應該要有做野幫過手足 <br />\n<br />\n西環山道間永利咁 <br />\n有人話黃 但都有人出黎反駁話聽到撐警言論<br />\n呢啲立場不定 老細又話怕表態既 根本就唔值得派貼紙<br />\n呢啲舖乜都無做過 同唇茶個啲捐錢出心出力既都有貼紙 公平咩？<br />\n<br />\n跪求正視下呢個問題"},{"pid":"251ddd765bcf8851a443866ae5487f92b13fd719","tid":1686302,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:48:20.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"69b0b3d4d380cb08de0f75de7a303cb03a0fa7d3","tid":1686302,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:50:27.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"babbce303cdcf08c83cf1e9ddbb93c617946d915","tid":1686302,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:51:32.000Z","msg":"真 <br />\n起碼都有連農先"},{"pid":"30753b38d8e7f3ee25f89d1f1a56ceafadf276f1","tid":1686302,"uid":12348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T05:11:10.000Z","msg":"山道咁多偽黃嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://neoguidehk.com/shop/no-milkshake-no-life/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fneoguidehk.com%2Fshop%2Fno-milkshake-no-life%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvDcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=f9f74e87\" target=\"_blank\">https://neoguidehk.com/shop/no-milkshake-no-life/</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c76c25374c3d8dd5dfefa97487f3edd24e94b08","tid":1686302,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T05:29:09.000Z","msg":"毛甴